    "If the user provides a list of liked papers, then these papers along with their referenced papers create a bigger set of papers that are the ground truth data for the artificial users.",
    "ResultsWe run the three RS versions for each user and compare the resulting Recall scores while making 50 recommendations each time (k=50).",
    "The results (Recall and NDCG scores) are presented in Tables 10 and 11, respectively.The system version #3 achieves the best performance in 50% of the tests (5/10 users).",
